title: Australia tab tom npaj yuav hno tshuaj COVID-19 txhab ntxiv. Now yog qhia tias yuav zoo li cas.
author: Biwa Kwan
description: Pib txij hnub tim 11.10.2021 mus ces muaj ib txhia neeg ntawm teb chaws Australia yuav muaj peev xwm hno tshuaj COVID-19 vaccine koob 3 lawm, los yog koob tshuaj sawv daws paub hu ua 'booster shot', kom thiaj li pov puag lawv ntawm tus kab mob COVID-19 tau zoo dua. Nod yog tej uas peb paub dhau los.
cleaned_text: Australia tej tau tshuaj COVID-19 vaccine koob 3 (booster shot) tau. Daim list no ces at the Boondall mass vaccination hub in Brisbane on 18 September 2021. ces 2 tag li ntawm 8 lub hli.
